      "title": "Enforce uniform card height on Home Screen project list",
      "description": "All project cards on the Home Screen must render at the same height regardless of content length (project name, phase, progress). Use CSS `grid` with equal-row sizing or flexbox with a fixed minimum height so that cards in each row align visually. Acceptance criteria: (1) All visible project cards in a row share the same rendered height. (2) Cards with short names and cards with long/wrapping names are the same height. (3) Verified at common breakpoints (mobile, tablet, desktop).",
